break-spaces;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare   \" id=\"SE-7252a5ad-07fa-11ec-912b-c96d0e2d1a3c\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: se-nanumsquare, \"\\\\B098눔고딕\", nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo;\">파주 임진각과 임진각평화누리공원은 살짝 거리가 있어요. 공원이 그만큼 넓기 때문이죠. 임진각은 지상 3층, 지하 1층으로 구성된 건물이고 임진각평화누리공원은 넓은 잔디광장입니다. </span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" id=\"SE-39e2c63a-755e-4fc8-91ec-36cff74b4461\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 2; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: break-spaces;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare   \" id=\"SE-7252a5ae-07fa-11ec-912b-9372d2c4db39\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: se-nanumsquare, \"\\\\B098눔고딕\", nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" id=\"SE-693c07ba-7fe7-4062-abad-3cae6e7710b0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 2; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: break-spaces;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare   \" id=\"SE-7252a5af-07fa-11ec-912b-49e60d477ea8\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: se-nanumsquare, \"\\\\B098눔고딕\", nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" id=\"SE-668040cf-16fd-4e43-b3de-31323c363ea1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 2; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: break-spaces;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare   \" id=\"SE-7252a5b0-07fa-11ec-912b-2f5bb5d09b0d\" style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: se-nanumsquare, \"\\\\B098눔고딕\", nanumgothic, sans-serif, Meiryo;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" id=\"SE-7252a5b2-07fa-11ec-912b-0f143a54923e\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 2; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: break-spaces;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumsquare   \" id=\"SE-7252a5b1-07fa-11ec-91