t=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_pohang_spacewalk_3.jpg 801w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_pohang_spacewalk_3-240x300.jpg 240w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_pohang_spacewalk_3-768x959.jpg 768w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_pohang_spacewalk_3-721x900.jpg 721w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_pohang_spacewalk_3-320x400.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 801px) 100vw, 801px\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-16258\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: right; font-size: 12px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">Credit:@uiland.kr</figcaption></figure><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: \"Noto Sans\"; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 30px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">총 333m 길이의 철 구조물 트랙을 따라 걸으며 환호공원과 포항제철소, 영일만, 영일대해수욕장 등 주변 풍광을 한눈에 볼 수 있다.</p><figure id=\"attachment_16259\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16259\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin: 30px auto; clear: both; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: italic; font-family: \"Noto Sans\"; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; width: 900px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16259\" src=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_pohang_spacewalk_4.jpg\" alt=\"포항 환호공원 스페이스워크\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_pohang_spacewalk_4.jpg 900w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_pohang_spacewalk_4-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_pohang_spacewalk_4-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_pohang_spacewalk_4-768x768.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-16259\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: right; font-size: 12px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">Credit:@retr1p</figcaption></figure><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: \"Noto Sans\"; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 30px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">철로 그려진 우아한 곡선과 밤하늘을 수놓은 조명은 철과 빛의 도시 포항을 상징한다고. 특히 스페이스워크에서 내려다보는 포항의 야경은 어디에서도 느낄 수 없는 특별한 경험을 제공할 것이니 놓치지 말자.</p><figure id=\"attachment_16260\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16260\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin: 30px auto; clear: both; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: italic; font-family: \"Noto Sans\"; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; width: 900px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16260\" src=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_pohang_spacewalk_5.jpg\" alt=\"포항 환호공원 스페이스워크\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/u