le=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><span style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 10pt; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><span style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: 700; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">– 문의 : </span>054-270-5561</span></p>','경북 포항시 북구 삼호로 370',NULL,'0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1',4,1,'/2022/11/22/s_6b15d40c-f90b-440c-b750-43ec78ae0132_hwanho_park_img01.jpg','36.066983085242','129.389169128428','2022-11-22 10:08:57','2022-11-26 18:56:20'),(112,33,'place_reviews','울진 죽변해안스카이레일 이용 후기 :: 해안 스카이레일 주차장, 가격, 시간 확인 / 울진','울진 죽변해안스카이레일','<figure id=\"attachment_16261\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16261\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin: 30px auto; clear: both; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: italic; font-family: \"Noto Sans\"; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; width: 873px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16261\" src=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_1.jpg\" alt=\"울진 죽변해안스카이레일\" width=\"873\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_1.jpg 873w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_1-262x300.jpg 262w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_1-768x880.jpg 768w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_1-786x900.jpg 786w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 873px) 100vw, 873px\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-16261\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: right; font-size: 12px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">Credit:@k_mikkk</figcaption></figure><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: \"Noto Sans\"; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 30px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">울진의 바다와 하늘이 맞닿는 곳에는 죽변해안스카이레일이 있다. 죽변 승하차장과 후정 승하차장을 오가는 4.8km의 코스로, 자동으로 움직이는 모노레일을 타고 바다를 가장 가까이서 바라볼 수 있다.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 16px; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"> </span></p><figure id=\"attachment_16262\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16262\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin: 30px auto; clear: both; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: italic; font-family: \"Noto Sans\"; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; width: 871px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16262\" src=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_2.jpg\" alt=\"울진 죽변해안스카이레일\" width=\"871\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_2.jpg 871w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_2-261x300.jpg 261w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_2-768x882.jpg 768w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_2-784x900.jpg 784w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 871px) 100vw, 871px\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-16262\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: right; font-size: 12px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">Credit:@k_mikkk</figcaption></figure><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: \"Noto Sans\"; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 30px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">겨울 바다를 사랑하지만, 추운 계절 매서운 바람이 두려웠던 이들도 스카이레일 안에서는 보다 따뜻하게 담을 수 있을 것이다. 유리창 너머로 보이는 하얀 등대와 그 아래 눈부신 파도는 조화롭게 어우러지고, 여기에 푸른 산이 더해지니 답답했던 가슴이 뻥 뚫리는 듯하다.</p><figure id=\"attachment_16263\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16263\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin: 30px auto; clear: both; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: italic; font-family: \"Noto Sans\"; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; width: 871px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16263\" src=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_3.jpg\" alt=\"울진 죽변해안스카이레일\" width=\"871\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_3.jpg 871w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_3-261x300.jpg 261w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_3-768x882.jpg 768w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_3-784x900.jpg 784w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 871px) 100vw, 871px\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-16263\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: right; font-size: 12px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">Credit:@k_mikkk</figcaption></figure><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: \"Noto Sans\"; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 30px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><span style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">바다 위를 달리다 보면 파도가 하트 모양으로 밀려 들어오는 하트해변의 모습을 볼 수 있다. 인위적으로 만든 것이 아닌, 파도가 밀려오고 나가며 자연적으로 형성되었다고 한다. 스카이레일에서 바라볼 때 가장 예쁘고 정확한 하트 모양을 담을 수 있다고 하니 사진은 필수다.</span></p><figure id=\"attachment_16264\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16264\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin: 30px auto; clear: both; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: italic; font-family: \"Noto Sans\"; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; width: 871px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16264\" src=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_4.jpg\" alt=\"울진 죽변해안스카이레일\" width=\"871\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_4.jpg 871w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_4-261x300.jpg 261w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_4-768x882.jpg 768w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_uljin_skyrail_4-784x900.jpg 784w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 871p