h; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: italic; font-family: \"Noto Sans\"; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; width: 900px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16270\" src=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_geoje_jungledome_1.jpg\" alt=\"거제 식물원 정글돔\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_geoje_jungledome_1.jpg 900w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_geoje_jungledome_1-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_geoje_jungledome_1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_geoje_jungledome_1-768x768.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-16270\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: right; font-size: 12px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">Credit:@male_no.80491</figcaption></figure><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: \"Noto Sans\"; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 30px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">사계절 다양한 식물이 자라는 국내 최대 온실의 거제 식물원. 지역의 식물 생태계를 비롯해 등 다양한 환경의 식물을 한눈에 관찰하고 체험해 볼 수 있는 휴식공간이다. 열대온실의 거제정글돔, 야외생태정원, 수생정원, 석부작정원, 잔디광장, 편의시설 등으로 구성되어 있다.</p><figure id=\"attachment_16271\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16271\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin: 30px auto; clear: both; max-widt