; font-size: 16px; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"> </span></p><figure id=\"attachment_16272\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16272\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin: 30px auto; clear: both; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-style: italic; font-family: \"Noto Sans\"; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; width: 900px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16272\" src=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_geoje_jungledome_3.jpg\" alt=\"거제 식물원 정글돔\" width=\"900\" height=\"974\" srcset=\"https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_geoje_jungledome_3.jpg 900w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_geoje_jungledome_3-277x300.jpg 277w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_geoje_jungledome_3-768x831.jpg 768w, https://www.kkday.com/ko/blog/wp-content/uploads/korea_geoje_jungledome_3-832x900.jpg 832w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; height: auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-16272\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: right; font-size: 12px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">Credit:@sang_9uu</figcaption></figure><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: \"Noto Sans\"; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 30px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">지난달에 정글타워라는 국내 최대 미끄럼틀이 생겨 5종류의 스릴을 느껴볼 수 있다. 이곳의 트레이드마크라 할 수 있는 새둥지 포토존도 